{"tid":1526882,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"9月2號7點請大家番母校 呼籲師弟師妹罷課","createTime":"2019-09-01T07:52:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T16:35:04.000Z","uid":126740,"like":85,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"aab320b45494a6c4fa9f33d0575fbfcffb2f5dac","tid":1526882,"uid":126740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T07:52:29.000Z","msg":"文宣組：聽日0700左右準備 起學校門口派傳單呼籲咁多位師弟師妹離開<br />\n一間學校只要有一位巴絲企出黎就得 <br />\n好多師弟師妹都過唔到爸媽果關 <br />\n希望我地班哥哥 姐姐可以係最後推佢地一把<br />\n 比d勇氣佢地<br />\n<br />\n另外冇勇氣走既師弟師妹 唔好怪佢地 <br />\n希望咁多位哥哥姐姐 <br />\n可以係學校外面叫口號 張聲音帶入母校 <br />\n比師弟師妹聽<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"10c87069bd36138d0b112d369231e7bc0d704fa9","tid":1526882,"uid":126740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T07:52:46.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"d6ad2ec1d005fe15bfef9efa2f30f561feac9387","tid":1526882,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T07:52:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dbb0567af8f83b1b39c09045f66cc32a5449e396","tid":1526882,"uid":126740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T07:53:01.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"bc9b8e9ca516f3c6760b35bb43ed03f0168d502c","tid":1526882,"uid":126740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T07:53:14.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"d77b7eecee942d9a8c28c8b806c19a9cd23dcec2","tid":1526882,"uid":126740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T07:53:28.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"7418d3e1725e5ba37efdcaccc52a1ba6cf0435c2","tid":1526882,"uid":126740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T07:53:40.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"8c8cf937f6c846ba20377262ae94d78c542543a8","tid":1526882,"uid":126740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T07:53:55.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"e9f5ea9c693b03503e0ffafb193f51ca5ab33076","tid":1526882,"uid":251083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T07:54:06.000Z","msg"