k\">https://lih.kg/1523089</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n當年有份聯署既人，大部分都走哂，仲留得係度既人，你都估到佢係咩人？？<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有人性嘅，應該一早 劈炮，唔再做 cctvb吧！但係佢仲要做足7年，做到2019 年今日，然後佢想洗白拎光環，叫3毛 錢7開post造勢，想拎光環夾橫行直入海關警察入境. 繼續染紅政府為藍屍發聲。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n我心裡梗係想佢係因良心發現而辭職啦<br />\n佢係鬼良心發現辭職咩<br />\n係<em>比</em>班同事投訴佢番工唔做野掛住化妝<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">覺得比人杯先辭渣<br />\n仲帶哂光環咁<br />\n屋企警察世家攞咩光環<br />\n<br />\n最後 cctvb假新聞記者主播無一個無辜 <br />\n唔好亂信任何消息 為佢哋洗白<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑警 主播 死 全 家</span></span>"},{"pid":"a4d37ef5391cf3c142c39edf498acf2f36aec2be","tid":1526882,"uid":79532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T07:58:48.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"9bbcbc86b283dca5f69d8b873a9a90c70d7e8e5d","tid":1526882,"uid":60578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f53a34113ebd136c1f4efe5f2a66298cdad43771","tid":1526882,"uid":136249,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T07:56:24.000Z","msg":"叫佢地番去招呼狗仔女仲好啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T07:59:10.000Z","msg":"做左9 2先 日後大班時間慢慢招呼"},{"pid":"bd7f116df1562b3f521110086da502cd9c06ea4c","tid":1526882,"uid":79532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T07:59:25.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"396b7babf4bfd0e223e99590acf6179e119126a7","tid":1526882,"uid":79532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T07:59:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b88362d6c5390ba4127664c25a2e9db0a7f98d1a","tid":1526882,"uid":126740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:06:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"39a2e4e55a5969d4ac74bbd047cf6616e05d0253","tid":1526882,"uid":126740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T